Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda/realtek: Apply headset jack quirk for non-bass alc287 thinkpads
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 2468e8922d2f6da81a6192b73023eff67e3fefdd
